{"id":646517,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/06/【立此存照】中央和国家机关党员工作时间之外政/","date":"2020-06-07T00:28:18Z","modified":"2020-06-07T06:20:50Z","title":"【立此存照】中央和国家机关党员工作时间之外政治言行若干规定","content":"<p>CDT编者按：近日，中央和国务院机关工委发布文件《关于印发&lt;中央和国家机关党员工作时间之外政治言行若干规定（试行）&gt;的通知》，该试行规定一连规定了18个“不准”：在“任何场合”——意味着包括私人场合——不准说不同意见。特别点明“不准发表偏离“两个维护”的言论，不准点赞，不准浏览“反动网站”；不准“收听收看境外反动电台和电视节目”……</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-646518\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/1-2.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"929\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/1-2.jpeg 646w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/1-2-162x300.jpeg 162w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/1-2-551x1024.jpeg 551w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-646519\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/2-1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"870\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/2-1.jpeg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/2-1-173x300.jpeg 173w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/2-1-589x1024.jpeg 589w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-646520\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/3-1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"996\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/3-1.jpeg 602w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/3-1-151x300.jpeg 151w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/3-1-514x1024.jpeg 514w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n","author":997,"categories":[18271,38912,38944],"tags":[40775,12306,40774,40776]}